<plot>Film Trix 2002 is the first in a series of documentary shorts consisting of interviews with filmmakers at various film-related events. Film Trix 2002 was shot in Park City, Utah, during the 2002 Sundance Film Festival. Christie Pesicka, an independent filmmaker herself, interviews filmmakers, actors, and festival personnel to explore the entire process of developing, shooting, promoting, and distributing independent films.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?194272</url></doc>
